  <brief_title>Safety Study of GRNOPC1 in Spinal Cord Injury</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1 Safety Study of GRNOPC1 in Patients With Neurologically Complete, Subacute, Spinal Cord Injury</official_title>
  <sponsors>
