  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the safety of GRNOPC1 administered at a single
      time-point between 7 and 14 days post injury, inclusive, to patients with neurologically
      complete spinal cord injuries (SCI).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
